===============================================================================
                                ActsAsAudited
===============================================================================

acts_as_audited is an ActiveRecord extension that logs all changes to your
model in an audits table.

    class User < ActiveRecord::Base
      acts_as_audited :except => [:password, :mistress]
    end

See http://opensoul.org/2006/07/21/acts_as_audited for more information.

 Installation
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Install the plugin into your rails app

     script/plugin install \
       http://source.collectiveidea.com/public/rails/plugins/acts_as_audited

2. Copy db/migration.rb into a new migration and run it.